  "title": "Part-Time Cleaner (Marina Square Retail Outlet)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Location:</strong> Marina Square – Gain City<br /><strong>Working Hours:</strong> Daily, <strong>11:00 AM – 2:00 PM (3 hours)</strong></p><h3><strong>Job Scope</strong></h3><p><strong>Cleaning Duties</strong></p><ul><li><p>Sweep and mop the floor in the <strong>Small Appliances</strong> and <strong>Big Appliances</strong> working areas.</p></li><li><p>Wipe and clean:</p><ul><li><p>Workstations and display tables</p></li><li><p>Appliance surfaces and counters</p></li></ul></li><li><p>Ensure the work areas are <strong>neat, tidy, and presentable</strong> at all times.</p></li><li><p>Empty rubbish bins and dispose of waste properly.</p></li><li><p>Light cleaning of nearby common areas if required.</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><p><p>Able to work independently and follow simple instructions<br /><br />Physically fit to perform basic cleaning tasks.</p><p>Neat, responsible, and punctual.</p><p>Friendly and professional attitude.<br /></p><p>Note:<br />Please Whatsapp message <strong>\"Part-Time Cleaner (Marina Square Retail Outlet)\"</strong> to 94793875 to discuss further details</p></p>",
